Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,庙会的准备很顺利哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也会用好东西给你尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大人版区长 还有小玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 在市内巡逻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看来很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正要去茱莉小姐那边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,做感冒的巩固检查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,上次光顾着水奈和火奈 忘记给我检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,区长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会儿要去和都内的大人物开会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 所以变大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要离开这个区 迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能抽烟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 这样只在这市里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这两位关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦 对了阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是今晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 又将是一个漫长的夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:46.29,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:51.00,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.38,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}やあ また会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.76,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ねぇ こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.67,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}いや こんにちはだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.22,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}広いようで 狭いようで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.93,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}退屈はいらないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}あぁ 問題は依然あって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}頭痛いんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.27,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}少しずつって言い聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.44,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}願い事叶えて行きましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:16.49,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}I shall remember I wanna do I shall remember
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:22.33,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}拾い集めた後悔のかけらたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}夜が明ける前に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何遍を貼って 並べてて 希望に変える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.13,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}10秒継続中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.13,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}桜が去つて散ったその後で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.93,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何が真実なのかは かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.76,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody そう今は奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.68,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}愛が世界救うのだなんて 僕は信じてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.36,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今 目の前の君が 明日を生きれるくらいには
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.15,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不条理は吹き飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.44,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀楽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.91,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}大丈夫さ　どこまでもゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:07.37,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalala　lalalalalala!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.15,opch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.38,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呀啊 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.76,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.67,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不 应该是中午好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.22,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}好像很宽敞 又好像很拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.93,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过貌似和「无聊」二字无缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}啊 问题依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.27,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过还是向我慢慢道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.44,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我们一起去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:22.33,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将散落一地的后悔的碎片小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在天明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}一遍遍地粘合 一遍遍地重排 将之变为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.13,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}持续10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.13,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在那满树樱花逝去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.93,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}什么才是真实 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.76,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody 没错 现在就奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.68,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}都说爱会拯救世界 我可一点都不信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.36,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}现在 眼前的你 想要享受明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.15,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}先把不合理统统打飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.44,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.91,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}放心吧 我们无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,又惹桃华生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,话说有什么不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想一起逛庙会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一群女生一起逛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一脸不开心啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是跟女朋友吵架了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…呃不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是跟妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦 真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦 嘛嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦 嘛嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行 不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹啊 妹妹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要疼爱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好男人 所以这算特殊服务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}变魔术?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…啊不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有机关也没有障眼法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐 我又来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又在吃东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做感冒的巩固检查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦 之前忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,食欲如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这就结束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有食欲就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…啊 既然茱莉小姐这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的诊查结束咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这是茱莉小姐的家人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,英国那边 你已经好多年没回去过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得孤单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈都有寄信来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不算孤单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而且妈妈的博客我也偶尔在看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,博客?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好高端洋气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢…奶奶也已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不太清楚家人是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 阿姬的父母是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,空白的一代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝和言叶的父母也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这么说 但那时还没懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,连他们相貌都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要说孤单…也有些乖乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,该算什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 父亲他们是怀着什么样的心情做下如此决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,以及在我们这一代人身上寄托了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我都还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这么伤感啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,回到家里有恭助和桃华在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝和铃就像妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然蓝有时候会像老妈似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上八重小姐 小玛丽 茱莉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的大姐姐也有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有什么孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就热闹非常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去阿姬家做顿好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我可爱的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,火锅可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 超喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,锦上添大葱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是大葱 是花束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是锦…是恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,呀啊 掉下来了掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是跑了好远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个身体目前只有一半是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但总有一天要完全据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这就是另一个次元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是有够乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只要想办法让这副身体完全妖怪化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这种世界手到擒来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便给它配音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看你这么大个人还玩布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太温馨了 忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快去完成你的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,半妖的猎人小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦 事前调查是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 真是个事多的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也还没适应这个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你是个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到挺聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 我确实还没出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,算是试运行中 磨合期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对了你是引擎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(699,659)}円     神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是引擎…你是引擎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(760,659)}円     神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\pos(560,659)}円     神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那么那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你这耳朵是不是冷却系统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,切下来会不会发奇热来?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,笑个不停的烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不止能让你堕化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还能把你送走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要刺穿你的心脏也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊 可惜可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果刀身能再长一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就能刺到心脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 这是魔法还是咒术?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成是魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有机关也没有障眼法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我没空陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,理由很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 再往右边点?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还是左边…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢啊 小恭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为茱莉小姐最懂花了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,卡特兰 鸡蛋花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大波斯菊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还有樱草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,花语是「永远的爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐知道的好多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,跟桃华吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么把这个给她就没 ~ 问 ~ 题 ~ 了 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,花儿是有魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要珍视自己的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐有兄弟姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,准确地说是曾经有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她死掉了…在小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 就是这张牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐刚才选的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快瞧啊 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 就只有这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让姐姐看厉害的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 快看 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有机关也没有障眼法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术超越了感动 变成一种恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我开始排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一天 恐怖的对象不再是魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我和姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,凑成一对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}呐 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来宛如长满荆棘的黑玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕着这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}呐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这恐怖很快消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 应该说变成了永远无法消失的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她突然…离开了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我到现在也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为当了医生能知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,结果完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,正好也想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 别消沉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,说过的吧 现在就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点都不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名的联络?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 说是怪物的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,水奈火奈也提到过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,据说有多名居民目击到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但可能是妖怪猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶她们好像已经去巡逻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,同为半妖所以能分辨出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,都说让他联络我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你手机打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院所以关机了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去巡逻一圈再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是个轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,诶? 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怪物用网兜能抓到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,网兜?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,网兜是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,绿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好有正义伙伴范儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个拐角对面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶 来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,巡逻的时候感觉到半妖的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,石榴也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,枝垂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 云珠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你让总代独自一人去了都内会议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我有研究没做完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总代也说一个人更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,椎名君 能冲两杯咖啡来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不加糖和奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我本就不适合那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样搞研究更合我胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抛头露面这种事实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你是元老院最能干的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不否认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都老大不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自己有多少实力还是心知肚明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,反省短处固然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但发扬长处也有同样分量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为了做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,又是现学现卖的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁来着呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,云珠 你也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是空白的一代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也是这个世界的蜗居者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不是在责备你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为了做自己能做的事出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的是将阴阳道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,将科学的全部精髓解读
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我只有这么点本事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是完全搞不通其中奥妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看这些就像是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,接通电源 电脑启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去如此简单的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其中却包含了大量高深的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 绝大部分人把这个流程当做天经地义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果觉得魔法不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,科学也一样不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,过分先进的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和魔法并无二致
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是很有名的言论
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 二者有决定性的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别卖关子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,科学和魔术一样 是有机关的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这盒子是机关与障眼法的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人们将如魔术般不可思议之事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,被科学哄骗着度过每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以说是一种傲慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,被科学哄骗着度过每一天…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?是那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自以为是我姐姐的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,隔了好久终于能见到姐姐的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今天心情超级好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就什么都不对你做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只拿回姐姐就全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟姐姐的二人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹 如果现在还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想见她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想见个面看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不相见吧…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个实在…呐 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,莉菈?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.42,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:03.00,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将时钟的指针拨反过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.84,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在梦中轻轻啜泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:09.64,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我又开始了今天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.19,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢谈天说地却讨厌侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.82,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢品尝美食却讨厌亲手烹调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:32.45,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}能包容你如此任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.16,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}全世界就只有我一人 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.83,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}这眼泪是为谁而流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.46,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}为我吗 亦或是为你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:47.17,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}流干眼泪之后又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:50.80,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}还是想和谁在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.31,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.93,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}听我讲述昨夜的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.86,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在这个破除了魔法的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:05.28,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我四处搜寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.99,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:12.57,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我听一听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:19.29,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}再次将我带入甜美的梦乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:59.42,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:03.00,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}时计の针を逆さまに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.84,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:09.64,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今日もまた 仆は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.19,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}おしゃべりがすき 闻くのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.82,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}食べることがすき 作るのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:32.45,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}そんなわがままが通じるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.16,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}世界で仆だけと知っていたかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.83,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}この涙は 谁のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.46,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆のためか 君のためか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:47.17,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}カラカラになってそれからまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:50.80,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}谁かといたいと思えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.31,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.93,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}昨日までの梦のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:01.86,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}魔法がとけたこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:05.28,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆は君を探したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.99,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:12.57,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}君の声を闻かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:19.29,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦の中でもう一度 连れていくよ
